This project is a fully responsive and modern cleaning service website developed using HTML5, CSS3, Bootstrap 5, and Font Awesome. The website is designed to provide a professional online presence for a cleaning company with visually appealing layouts, smooth responsiveness, and user-friendly sections.

The project includes a beautifully designed hero section with a background image overlay, responsive navigation bar, service showcase, testimonials, pricing plans, booking form, featured companies section, before & after cleaning showcase, workflow steps, and a detailed footer section. The interface follows a clean and elegant color scheme with proper alignment, spacing, and typography to create a premium user experience.

Key Features:
• Fully responsive design for desktop, tablet, and mobile devices
• Bootstrap 5 grid system and components integration
• Modern hero section with overlay effects and CTA buttons
• Responsive navigation bar with professional layout
• Interactive booking and estimate form UI
• Customer testimonials section using styled cards
• Services showcase with image-based layouts
• “How It Works” section with custom icons and steps
• Pricing plan card with highlighted premium package
• Clean typography using Google Fonts
• Font Awesome and SVG icons integration
• Consistent UI/UX design across all sections
• Structured and maintainable HTML & CSS code

Technologies Used:
• HTML5
• CSS3
• Bootstrap 5
• Font Awesome
• Google Fonts

This project demonstrates front-end development skills including responsive web design, Bootstrap customization, layout structuring, modern UI styling, and component-based webpage organization. It is suitable for portfolio showcase, internship tasks, and front-end practice projects.
